                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18360919-2123-offence-1 t18360919-cd-96"></join>26th of August</rs>, 6 Spoons, value 20<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18360919-name-646" type="victimName">
