                        <interp inst="t18360919-name-647" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD PURCELL</persName>
                  </hi>. I am assistant to Mr. Hedges, a pawnbroker. I produce six spoons pawned by the prisoner, in one lot, on the 26th of August.</p>
               <p>
